{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-079","title":"买围巾帽子","sectionId":"chapter-04","sectionTitle":"商店购物买买买","pageStart":407,"pageEnd":410,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":28,"duplicateEntryCount":7,"pages":[{"number":407,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"79 买围巾帽子"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"scarf [skɑːf]","headword":"scarf"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.围巾"},{"type":"note","text":"◎woolen scarf羊毛围巾/suede scarf软羔皮围巾"},{"type":"entry","text":"silk scarf丝绸围巾","headword":"silk scarf"},{"type":"entry","text":"pashmina [pæʃˈmiːnə]","headword":"pashmina"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.羊绒披肩"},{"type":"entry","text":"hat [hæt]","headword":"hat"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.帽子"},{"type":"entry","text":"top hat大礼帽","headword":"top hat"},{"type":"entry","text":"sun hat遮阳帽","headword":"sun hat"},{"type":"entry","text":"straw hat 草帽","headword":"straw hat"},{"type":"entry","text":"cowboy hat 牛仔帽","headword":"cowboy hat"}]},{"number":408,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"baseball cap 棒球帽","headword":"baseball cap"},{"type":"entry","text":"beret [ˈbereɪ]","headword":"beret"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.贝雷帽"},{"type":"entry","text":"rain hat 雨帽","headword":"rain hat"},{"type":"note","text":"◎bamboo rain hat笠帽"},{"type":"entry","text":"bucket hat 渔夫帽","headword":"bucket hat"},{"type":"entry","text":"bomber hat 雷锋帽","headword":"bomber hat"},{"type":"entry","text":"newsboy hat 报童帽","headword":"newsboy hat"},{"type":"entry","text":"balaclava [ˌbæləˈklɑːvə]","headword":"balaclava"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.巴拉克拉法帽"},{"type":"entry","text":"fedora [fɪˈdɔːrə]","headword":"fedora"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.软呢帽"},{"type":"text","text":"skullies &amp;amp; beanies 颅骨帽"},{"type":"entry","text":"visor [ˈvaɪzə(r)]","headword":"visor"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.（头盔上的）面甲，面罩，护面；遮阳帽舌"},{"type":"note","text":"◎sun visor（车辆驾驶室挡风玻璃上的）防晒板"},{"type":"entry","text":"bonnet [ˈbɒnɪt]","headword":"bonnet"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.（带子系于颌下的）童帽，旧式女帽"},{"type":"entry","text":"helmet [ˈhelmɪt]","headword":"helmet"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.头盔"},{"type":"note","text":"◎safety helmet安全帽/fire helmet救火头盔"}]},{"number":409,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"helmet shield焊工面罩","headword":"helmet shield"},{"type":"entry","text":"hat brim 帽边","headword":"hat brim"},{"type":"entry","text":"cap stretcher 帽撑","headword":"cap stretcher"},{"type":"entry","text":"hat ribbon 帽带","headword":"hat ribbon"},{"type":"entry","text":"single layer 单层","headword":"single layer"},{"type":"entry","text":"tassel [ˈtæsl]","headword":"tassel"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.流苏"},{"type":"entry","text":"broad-brimmed [ˌbrɔːdˈbrɪmd]","headword":"broad-brimmed"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.宽边的"},{"type":"entry","text":"elastic [ɪˈlæstɪk]","headword":"elastic"}]},{"number":410,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"a.弹性的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎elastic force弹力"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"text","text":"有趣的小词hat"},{"type":"text","text":"如果你和老外出去聚会，你很好奇地问Is it free? 结果老外却跟你"},{"type":"text","text":"说Pass the hat. 你会不会暗自嘀咕他（她）为什么要你“递帽子”呢？下"},{"type":"text","text":"面我们就讲讲hat的其他用法。"},{"type":"text","text":"1. Pass the hat. 大家出钱吧！"},{"type":"entry","text":"Pass the hat的意思是“大家出钱”，也可用pass the hat round，表","headword":"Pass the hat"},{"type":"text","text":"示“集资，筹款”，多用于为生病的同事或搞庆祝活动筹款。例如，你"},{"type":"text","text":"的同事阿曼达要结婚了，你希望和其他同事一起凑钱给她买礼物，就"},{"type":"text","text":"可以说Amanda will get married and we pass the hat round for her。这种"},{"type":"text","text":"情况就一定会用到put in或plug in，其意思是“出多少钱”，如："},{"type":"text","text":"Everybody puts in 5 dollars. （每人出5美元。）"},{"type":"text","text":"2. He is wearing two hats.他身兼两职。"}]}]}